<span>n</span><span>í</span><span> virtu</span><span>á</span><span>ln</span><span>í</span><span> asistence na va</span><span>š</span><span>em smartphonu. Od funkce, kter</span><span>á</span><span> dok</span><span>áž</span><span>e rozpoznat</span><span></span><em><span>v</span></em><em><span>áš</span></em><span></span><span>hlas p</span><span>ř</span><span>es prohled</span><span>á</span><span>v</span><span>á</span><span>n</span><span>í</span><span> v</span><span>ý</span><span>sledk</span><span>ů</span><span> </span><span>ž</span><span>iv</span><span>é</span><span>ho vyhled</span><span>á</span><span>v</span><span>á</span><span>n</span><span>í</span><span> a</span><span>ž</span><span> k</span><span></span><span>vyu</span><span>ží</span><span>v</span><span>á</span><span>n</span><span>í</span><span> p</span><span>ř</span><span>ede</span><span>š</span><span>l</span><span>é</span><span>ho chov</span><span>á</span><span>n</span><span>í</span><span> ke sd</span><span>í</span><span>len</span><span>í</span><span> v</span><span>ý</span><span>sledk</span><span>ů</span><span> mezi za</span><span>ří</span><span>zen</span><span>í</span><span>mi</span><span>&nbsp;–</span><span> to v</span><span>š</span><span>echno se odehr</span><span>á</span><span>v</span><span>á</span><span> okam</span><span>ž</span><span>it</span><span>ě</span><span> a</span><span></span><span>v</span><span>ě</span><span>t</span><span>š</span><span>ina z</span><span></span><span>n</span><span>á</span><span>s nikdy neuva</span><span>ž</span><span>uje o</span><span></span><span>tom,</span><span></span><em><span>jakou</span></em><span> funkci v</span><span></span><span>tom hraje um</span><span>ě</span><span>l</span><span>á</span><span> inteligence. Tease o</span><span>č</span><span>ek</span><span>á</span><span>v</span><span>á</span><span> podobn</span><span>ý</span><span> jev v</span><span></span><span>diagnostick</span><span>é</span><span> technice.</span></p> \n<p style=\"margin: 12pt 0in;\"><span>„</span><span>P<